<p>Using an RSS reader instead of visiting Youtube or other social media has many advantages, including that you have to deal with much less energy-sapping, will-eroding clickbait. Unfortunately feed entries can still have clickbaity titles that can DESTROY your patience! So I wrote a dumb-as-rocks declickbaiter for Elfeed. You WON&rsquo;T BELIEVE the results!</p>
<p>The Before (The After will SHOCK you!):
<img src="https://karthinks.com/img/declickbait-before-extra.png" alt=""></p>
<p>The After:
<img src="https://karthinks.com/img/declickbait-after-extra.png" alt=""></p>
<p>The Code:</p>
