</span></span></code></pre></div><p><code>elfeed-title-transform</code> can be replaced with something much better, like a grammar aware title formatter (AI or otherwise), or with information extracted from the content or video description of the entry. But I&rsquo;ll settle for this pareto solution for what was <a href="https://youtube.com/watch?v=tF4OdtSuXMg">half an hour of live coding</a> in the dark:</p>
